  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Public Outreach Rep",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Public Outreach Rep</strong></h2><p>👥 People • Events • Real Conversations</p><p>If you’re someone who values real connection, growth through experience, and meaningful work with people, this role might resonate with you.</p><p>At <strong>Vision Organisation</strong>, being a Public Outreach Rep isn’t about pushing products. It’s about showing up, engaging sincerely, and creating positive experiences through face-to-face interaction at events, roadshows, and public spaces.</p><p>This is active, people-focused work where you learn by doing, supported by a team that believes in growth, effort, and learning together.</p><h3><strong>🎯 What You’ll Be Doing</strong></h3><p>🎤 Represent client brands with honesty and professionalism<br />👋 Engage members of the public through respectful, friendly conversations<br />💬 Create genuine interactions that leave people feeling heard and valued<br />🤝 Work alongside a supportive team to deliver campaigns with care and consistency</p><h3><strong>🌟 What You’ll Get</strong></h3><p>🎓 Full training provided — experience is not required<br />📈 Growth based on effort, learning, and performance<br />🌍 Exposure to different campaigns, locations, and people<br />🤝 Coaching, mentorship, and a team that supports your development</p><h3><strong>🙌 Who This Role May Suit</strong></h3><p>Someone who enjoys meeting people and being present<br />Someone open to learning, feedback, and personal growth<br />Someone reliable, respectful, and team-oriented<br />Someone who prefers real-world experience over desk-bound routines</p><h3><strong>📩 How to Apply</strong></h3><p>If this sounds like something you’d like to explore, we’d be glad to connect.</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507</p>",
